snippet.title: Blossom Tales 2: The Minotaur Prince - Release Date and Boss Trailer
snippet.description:
Lily is BACK and craving adventure once more! Join her as she ventures across the land, tasked to defeat the Minotaur King and save her brother.

Blossom tales 2: The Minotaur Prince launches on August 16th on Steam and Nintendo Switch!

Wishlist on Steam today: https://bit.ly/BT2Steam

Follow Playtonic Friends and Castle Pixel on Twitter to be kept up-to-date with more news: 
Playtonic: https://twitter.com/PlaytonicGames
Castle Pixel: https://twitter.com/castlepixel

#GameTrailers #ReleaseDate #Switch
